{"type":"message","id":"daa77dc7","parentId":"54425399","timestamp":"2026-03-19T21:26:54.080Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_d7ee9135-a3f8-4d1e-adad-adf97dfdd6fc","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# 2026-03-19 — Memory Log\n\n## Session: Nava Post Creation + Relay Test\n\n### Current Context\n- Draft 001: \"Incentive Trap\" concept - post-first workflow\n- Draft complete and approved by Tiny\n- Testing browser relay - user skeptical of screenshot capability\n\n### Nava Content Docs (to read before each cycle)\nLocation: `docs/nava-content-system/`\nFiles:\n1. Nava Healthcare Content Bible.md\n2. Nava_Blog_Research_Notes.md\n3. Nava_Content_Thinking_Framework_MASTER.md\n4. Nava_Custom_GPT_Initial_Handoff_Instructions.md\n5. Nava_LinkedIn_X_Content_Guide.md\n6. Nava Case Studies.pdf\n\n### Nava Post Writing Style (2026-03-19 session)\n**DO:**\n- Write in flowing prose, not bullet-style one-liners\n- Cluster related ideas into single paragraphs with transitions (\"regardless\", \"yet\", \"but\")\n- Frame hypotheticals fairly: acknowledge the other side's valid arguments (don't build strawmen only to burn them down)\n- If mentioning Nava actions: be grounded in reality — \"we didn't chase X\" only if we actually did; otherwise \"Nice dream, but impractical\" works better\n- Use compressed sentences, short paragraphs, natural rhythm\n- Bold for narrative pivots only\n\n**DON'T:**\n- Write one-line paragraphs (looks AI-generated)\n- Use \"we stopped chasing X\" unless Nava actually chased it\n- Create arguments that are easy to knock down\n- Explain too much — trust the reader\n\n### Draft 001 Status\n- Concept: \"Incentive Trap\" - spread fee hypothetical → mic drop on zero upfront\n- Status: Draft complete, pending Tiny's final edits\n- Workflow: Post-first (image later)\n\n### Browser Relay\n- Status: Running on chrome-relay profile\n- Test: Navigating to Google to verify functionality\n\n### Key Reminders\n- Read nava-content-system docs before starting Nava work\n- Check existing posts in MEMORY.md to avoid duplicates\n- Nava appears late in posts: Problem → Insight → Industry → Nava\n## 21:00 SAST — Sprint Check-in\n\n- Core scope (crawl → synthesis → full RAG): COMPLETE/STABLE\n- Browser relay: working, chrome-relay screenshot confirmed LinkedIn open\n- Gmail Calendar access: still pending user setup\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773955614078}}
