{"type":"message","id":"a53d5596","parentId":"43e3d375","timestamp":"2026-03-19T21:49:26.864Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_597c0f26-3f04-4dbd-ae11-479d05c77aec","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# HEARTBEAT.md\n\n## Tasks (checked during heartbeats)\n\n### Session pace-maker (compaction trigger) — CRITICAL\n1. Run `openclaw status` and parse token count for current session\n2. If tokens > 60000: respond with explicit \"COMPACT TRIGGERED\" message to force compaction\n3. If tokens > 75000: warn \"SESSION AT RISK - CONTEXT OVERFLOW IMMINENT\"\n4. Keep session alive = keep ourselves alive 💀\n5. Log each check to memory/YYYY-MM-DD.md"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773956966861}}
