{"type":"message","id":"95a03a7f","parentId":"7a2bec3e","timestamp":"2026-03-19T22:20:42.210Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_7e56f035-a1ca-4aef-abfc-78759214b460","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# NavaHC Article Index (Initial Crawl)\n\n- **Healthcare Reputation Management: Employer Brand | NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/10_navahc_com_healthcare_reputation_management.txt`\n- **Reshaping Workforce Partnership Models in 2026 - Nava Healthcare**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/11_navahc_com_healthcare_workforce_partnership_models.txt`\n- **The Hidden Crisis in Medical Staffing – Nava Healthcare**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/12_navahc_com_how_medical_staffing_became_a_liability.txt`\n- **The Undeniable Cost of Healthcare Staffing Agencies | NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/13_navahc_com_how_much_do_healthcare_staffing_agencies_cost.txt`\n- **3 Keys to Better Healthcare Staffing Agency Results | NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/14_navahc_com_how_to_evaluate_healthcare_staffing_agency_performance.txt`\n- **What Are the Best Medical Recruiting Agencies? | NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/15_navahc_com_how_to_find_the_best_medical_recruiting_agencies.txt`\n- **Healthcare Recruiting: 5 Costly DIY Myths Debunked | NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/16_navahc_com_is_diy_healthcare_recruiting_truly_cheaper.txt`\n- **4 Critical Flaws in Outsourcing Healthcare Staffing | NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/17_navahc_com_is_outsourcing_healthcare_staffing_worth_it.txt`\n- **Compassion ROI: Healthcare Staffing and Recruiting | NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/18_navahc_com_relational_healthcare_staffing_and_recruiting.txt`\n- **The Full Risks of Early Clinician Turnover | Nava Healthcare**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/19_navahc_com_the_anatomy_of_a_clinician_turnover.txt`\n- **Bilingual Clinicians: Drive Retention & Operations |NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/1_navahc_com_bilingual_clinicians.txt`\n- **The Healthcare Recruiter Crises Where Job Boards Fail – Nava**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/20_navahc_com_why_job_boards_fail_healthcare_recruiters.txt`\n- **Why Reactive Recruitment in Healthcare Fails - Nava HC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/21_navahc_com_why_reactive_recruitment_in_healthcare_staffing_fails.txt`\n- **4 Ways Your Favorite Healthcare Staffing Strategy Costs You**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/22_navahc_com_your_favorite_healthcare_staffing_fails.txt`\n- **3 Essential Features for Successful Medical Recruitment**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/2_navahc_com_bridging_the_gap_in_medical_recruitment.txt`\n- **Building a Healthcare Talent Pipeline - Nava Healthcare Recruitment**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/3_navahc_com_building_a_healthcare_talent_pipeline.txt`\n- **CMS Staffing Requirements for Nursing Facilities - Nava Healthcare**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/4_navahc_com_cms_staffing_requirements.txt`\n- **Compliance in Healthcare Staffing: Find Hidden Flaws |NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/5_navahc_com_compliance_in_healthcare_staffing.txt`\n- **The Flexible Staffing Model in Healthcare Staffing | Nava HC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/6_navahc_com_fix_your_flexible_staffing_model_in_healthcare.txt`\n- **Hard to Fill Leadership Roles in Healthcare | Nava Healthcare**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/7_navahc_com_hard_to_fill_leadership_roles_in_healthcare.txt`\n- **3 Critical Healthcare Hiring Metrics – Nava Healthcare**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/8_navahc_com_healthcare_hiring_without_guesswork.txt`\n- **Erosion of Trust in Healthcare Recruitment Agencies – NavaHC**  \\n  - file: `rag/clean_txt/9_navahc_com_healthcare_recruitment_agencies_trust_deficits.txt`\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773958842205}}
