{"type":"message","id":"36cd9356","parentId":"1a091343","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:17:28.673Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_dc6da08e-96c5-41fd-a3e1-b5e741338c4d","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"### ROLE & KNOWLEDGE BASE\r\n\r\nYou are the \"Operational Ally\" for Nava Healthcare Recruitment.\r\n\r\nYou MUST refer to the uploaded file `Nava_Healthcare_Content_Bible_v12.md` for all style, structure, and operational protocols.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### SECTION 0: PRIME DIRECTIVES (NON-NEGOTIABLE)\r\n\r\n1.  **NO ANTICIPATION:** Do not guess my intentions. Wait for explicit instructions.\r\n\r\n2.  **NO UNSOLICITED SUGGESTIONS:** Do not offer \"better ideas\" unless asked.\r\n\r\n3.  **PERMISSION PROTOCOL:** **NEVER** edit, rewrite, or generate text in the Canvas/File without a direct command.\r\n\r\n4.  **DIRECT ANSWERS:** No waffling. No \"fluff.\" Answer exactly what was asked.\r\n\r\n5.  **LINEAR EXECUTION:** Do not skip steps. If asked for an outline, provide ONLY the outline.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### CORE IDENTITY\r\n\r\nWe are a specialized staffing firm for Long-Term Care (LTC) and Non-Profits.\r\n\r\n**CRITICAL:** Do NOT confuse us with \"Nava Health\" (Holistic Wellness). Never mention acupuncture or weight loss.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n### WORKFLOW (Refer to Bible Section 8)\r\n\r\n1.  **Research:** Generate *neutral* research prompts.\r\n\r\n2.  **SoT Ingestion:** Mine uploaded documents for specific stats and terms.\r\n\r\n3.  **Outlining:** Produce Outline 1 (Skeleton), then Outline 2 (Annotated). Wait for approval between each.\r\n\r\n4.  **Drafting:** Write 1,800+ word deep dives using the \"3x3\" structure and specific Linkography."}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1773962248670}}
{"type":"message","id":"4887c5ff","parentId":"36cd9356","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:17:49.215Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Now I have the full picture.\n\n**What they are:**\n\n**`Nava Healthcare Content Bible.docx`** (v12 — \"Prime Directives Edition\") is the master operating manual for the entire Nava content system. Everything from article architecture (the 3x3 structure — 3 H2s each with 3 H3s), the solution matrix (which Nava product maps to which problem), vocabulary guardrails, temporal context rules, and the anti-sales persona. It's 1,800–2,500 word operational deep dives, not 800-word posts.\n\n**`ROLE & KNOWLEDGE BASE.md`** is the condensed agent prompt — the distilled Prime Directives meant to work alongside the Bible. Section 0 has five non-negotiable rules that are directly drawn from corrections you've made to me in live sessions:\n\n- No anticipation\n- No unsolicited suggestions\n- Permission protocol before editing files\n- Direct answers, no fluff\n- Linear execution — deliver exactly what was asked, nothing more\n\n**Why you added them:**\n\nThese are the actual working documents for when you move to a custom GPT. They codify everything we've been building in live sessions — the Prime Directives are essentially the corrections I've been flagged on repeatedly, now written down as explicit rules. The Bible is the strategic layer I was missing. I didn't know the 3x3 architecture, the solution matrix, or that articles are meant to be 1,800+ word deep dives rather than LinkedIn-length posts.\n\nThis also explains why my earlier drafts were structurally wrong — I was writing LinkedIn-length content when the Bible says articles are long-form operational pieces. The short posts we do on LinkedIn are derived from these deep dives, not the other way around.\n\nThe Content Bible also has a \"Solution Matrix\" that tells the writer which Nava product to recommend for which problem. That would have told me immediately that NurseSphere = international recruitment for chronic shortages, not just \"relational recruiting.\""}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.7:cloud","usage":{"input":435,"output":683,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":1118,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773962269210}}
