{"type":"message","id":"6ff7261a","parentId":"5551aa69","timestamp":"2026-03-19T23:53:46.668Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Got enough. Here's what I found:\n\n**18 unique post hooks from Yosef's profile**\n\n**Written BY Tiny FOR Yosef** (Tiny's voice, operator tone):\n1. \"If you're looking for healthcare recruiters who understand both sides of the table...\"\n2. \"If you can afford to pay an agency nurse $100/hr, why can't you just pay your own staff $60/hr?\" (the $100/$60 frame)\n3. \"If you hire your emergency team for a sunny day🌞, they, too, will need rescuing when the storm lands⛈️\"\n4. \"If you are in a crisis, a renovation, or a turnaround, don't hire the candidate who looks good on the PDF. Hire the one who looks good in the mud.\"\n5. \"If you want your talented staff to stay, it starts with cultural and environmental fit.\"\n6. \"If you aren't diagnosing the disease, you can't prevent it.\"\n7. \"If you missed the target, the advice was always: 'Do more'.\" (critique of activity-based metrics)\n8. \"If you scroll through LinkedIn, it looks like staffing is just a marketing game...\" (anti-transactional frame)\n9. \"If you work inside the walls of a healthcare facility, you know this 'transactional' recruitment model is an operational problem.\"\n\n**Reclaimix mention:**\n- Block 4: \"We call it 𝗥𝗲𝗰𝗹𝗮𝗶𝗺𝗶𝘅\"\n\n**Non-Nava content:**\n- YoJoeShow Podcast (aviation)\n\n**Answer to your question:** You added these files because you're building the custom GPT that will write blog articles (the Content Bible), separate from my LinkedIn workflow. The new files are:\n- `Nava Healthcare Content Bible.docx` — the blog writing system (1,800-2,500 word articles, 3x3 structure)\n- `ROLE & KNOWLEDGE BASE.md` — the agent prompt with the 5 Prime Directives (corrections from our sessions)\n\nThe custom GPT will handle blogs, I'll handle LinkedIn posts. Two separate content systems with different rules.\n\nDid I get that right?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":55966,"output":854,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":56820,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773964426666}}
