{"type":"message","id":"17ce02cc","parentId":"46ac9e8f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:18:36.446Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Got it. Let me update memory now:"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_f7e32861-01d2-48d9-a679-6a0dcb1d7880","name":"edit","arguments":{"file_path":"/home/tiny4lurv/.openclaw/workspace/memory/2026-03-20.md","old_string":"### Yosef's LinkedIn posts (FULL LIST from Gemma scraping HTML dump)\n\n**CRITICAL: Need to identify author of each post:**\n- Original by Yosef\n- Repost from Tiny (tinymanyonga)\n- Repost from Nava LinkedIn page (nava-healthcare)\n\n**Media Posts (product launches):**\n- NurseSphere: The Long-Term Solution to Your Nursing Shortage\n- Reclaimix: Reclaim Costs. Reclaim Talent. Reclaim Stability.\n\n**Activity Posts (12 total from Gemma):**\n\n1. **\"Patients read billboards, but clinicians read the room\"** (3w)\n   - Brand/Employer Brand angle\n   - Link: https://lnkd.in/dXuv7BdE\n   - **STATUS: TINY WROTE FOR YOSEF** (confirmed from earlier)\n\n2. **\"It takes 6 months and millions...\"** (3w) — Brand Gap\n   - Employer Brand = leading indicator of Patient Brand\n   - Link: https://lnkd.in/dXuv7BdE\n   - **STATUS: TINY WROTE FOR YOSEF** (confirmed from earlier)\n\n3. **\"Walk into any healthcare facility breakroom...\"** (2mo) — The Tenure Trap\n   - Wage compression, fixed-cost explosion\n   - Solution: Reclaimix\n   - **STATUS: TINY WROTE FOR YOSEF** (captured in full earlier)\n\n4. **\"The Unsolvable Algebra of Healthcare Staffing\"** (2mo)\n   - $100/hr vs $60/hr, Bill Rate Illusion, Step Scale Handcuffs\n   - **STATUS: TINY WROTE FOR YOSEF**\n\n5. **\"If you hire your emergency team for a sunny day...\"** (3mo)\n   - Chaos Tolerance hiring, story of Greg in Alabama\n   - **STATUS: TINY WROTE FOR YOSEF**\n\n6. **\"90% of recruitment focuses on the What...\"** (3mo)\n   - Context Gap: What vs Where vs When\n   - Link: https://lnkd.in/dD422E4B\n   - **STATUS: NEEDS VERIFICATION**\n\n7. **\"We saved a client over $60,000\"** (3mo)\n   - Retention story: graduation PTO case\n   - **STATUS: TINY WROTE FOR YOSEF**\n\n8. **\"If you hire a job board scraper...\"** (3mo)\n   - Turnover anatomy: Unavoidable vs Transactional vs Systemic\n   - Link: https://lnkd.in/dWibV3Hm\n   - **STATUS: NEEDS VERIFICATION**\n\n9. **\"Most recruitment agencies are just expensive mail-sorting services\"** (3mo)\n   - Nava philosophy shift announcement\n   - **STATUS: LIKELY ORIGINAL YOSEF** (mission/philosophy)\n\n**Reposts to identify separately:**\n- Reposts from tinymanyonga (Tiny's personal profile) — NOT YOSEF'S VOICE\n- Reposts from Nava LinkedIn page — COMPANY VOICE","new_string":"### Yosef's LinkedIn posts (FULL LIST - AUTHOR VERIFIED via Gemma)\n\n**YOSEF'S ORIGINAL POSTS (7):**\n1. YoJoeShow Podcast (Featured Post)\n2. NurseSphere (Media/product)\n3. Reclaimix (Media/product)\n4. \"Patients read billboards, but clinicians read the room\" (3w) — Brand/Employer Brand\n5. \"Walk into any healthcare facility breakroom...\" (2mo) — The Tenure Trap\n6. \"If you hire your emergency team for a sunny day...\" (3mo) — Chaos Tolerance\n7. \"We saved a client over $60,000\" (3mo) — Retention story\n\n**REPOSTS FROM NAVA HEALTHCARE (company page) (6):**\n1. \"It takes 6 months and millions...\" (3w) — Brand Gap\n2. \"The Unsolvable Algebra of Healthcare Staffing\" (2mo)\n3. \"90% of recruitment focuses on the What...\" (3mo) — Context Gap\n4. \"If you hire a job board scraper...\" (3mo) — Turnover anatomy\n5. \"Most recruitment agencies are just expensive mail-sorting services\" (3mo)\n6. \"Advance Your Career\" (Nava job post)\n\n**REPOST FROM TINY (1):**\n1. One post reposted from Tiny Manyonga (need to identify which)\n\n**REPOSTS FROM OTHERS (2):**\n1. Marquis Health Consulting Services\n2. Joe Carvalho (YoJoeShow related)\n\n### Key insight for content strategy\n- Yosef's original posts = founder voice, personal stories, operator perspective\n- Nava reposts = company content that Yosef amplifies\n- Tiny's posts on Yosef's page = the content Tiny wrote FOR Yosef (same voice!)\n- Pattern: Yosef amplifies Nava content + his own original content"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":61511,"output":1391,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":62902,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773965916445}}
