{"type":"message","id":"6b589e94","parentId":"1d998104","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:23:09.837Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Updated and committed. \n\nSo:\n- **Pattern A**: Tiny writes → Tiny posts to Tiny's profile → Yosef **reposts** (shows \"Yosef reposted this Tiny Manyonga\") — the screenshots show this\n- **Pattern B**: Tiny writes FOR Yosef → Yosef posts directly as himself (no repost tag) — this is what we did with Draft 001\n\nBoth work — depends on whether you want your voice visible (repost) or Yosef's voice standalone (direct post).\n\nIs that closer to what you meant?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":65518,"output":131,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":65649,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773966189836}}
