eposts from Tiny: 1 (\"Volume Trap\" - sales/recruitment philosophy)\n- Reposts from others: 2 (Marquis Health, Joe Carvalho/Podcast)\n\n**INSIGHTS — Tiny vs Yosef vs Nava patterns:**\n- **Yosef original**: Personal operator anecdotes, founder voice, story-driven (Greg story, $60k save)\n- **Nava reposts**: Conceptual frameworks (\"Brand Gap\", \"Unsolvable Algebra\"), educational, thought-leadership\n- **Tiny's reposted post**: \"Volume Trap\" - human instinct over AI automation\n- **Correction**: Earlier \"7 original by Yosef\" was wrong — some were Tiny-written-for-Yosef, not truly original\n\n**Key insight**: Yosef curates strategically — his original = personal stories; amplifies Nava = thought leadership; brings in Tiny = niche sales/recruitment perspectives"}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":21382,"output":822,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":22204,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773966713746}}
