{"type":"message","id":"219fced6","parentId":"50253066","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:33:49.891Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"toolCall","id":"ollama_call_1459fba2-810d-4cc0-b11b-7776b290dec4","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"python3 - <<'PY'\nimport base64, json, urllib.request, re\n\nhtml_path = \"/mnt/c/Users/Tiny4Lurv/Downloads/(26) Activity _ Yosef Roston _ LinkedIn.html\"\nwith open(html_path, \"r\", encoding=\"utf-8\") as f:\n    html = f.read()\n\n# Strip scripts and compress HTML for transmission\nhtml_clean = re.sub(r'<script[^>]*>.*?</script>', '', html, flags=re.DOTALL)\nhtml_clean = re.sub(r'<style[^>]*>.*?</style>', '', html_clean, flags=re.DOTALL)\n\n# Encode as base64 to avoid token issues\nhtml_b64 = base64.b64encode(html_clean[:80000].encode()).decode()\n\npayload = {\n    \"model\": \"qwen3.5:cloud\",\n    \"messages\": [{\n        \"role\": \"user\",\n        \"content\": f\"\"\"Analyze this LinkedIn profile HTML and count ALL posts.\n\nLook for the pattern in the HTML:\n- Original posts by Yosef Roston (he wrote it)\n- Reposts FROM Tiny Manyonga (Yosef reposted Tiny's content)\n- Reposts FROM Nava Healthcare Recruitment (Yosef reposted Nava's content)  \n- Reposts from OTHER sources\n\nFor each post, identify:\n1. Who is the ORIGINAL author (who wrote the content)\n2. Is it original OR a repost\n\nSearch the HTML for:\n- \"Tiny Manyonga\" mentions (these are reposts from Tiny)\n- \"Nava Healthcare\" mentions (these are reposts from Nava)\n- Look for the specific post topics to identify them\n\nList ALL posts you can identify with their authors.\n\nThen give final counts:\n- Total original posts by Yosef\n- Total reposts from Tiny\n- Total reposts from Nava  \n- Total reposts from other sources\n\nThis is the raw HTML of Yosef's LinkedIn activity page. Analyze it carefully.\n\nHTML (base64 encoded, first 80k chars):\n{html_b64}\"\"\"\n    }],\n    \"stream\": False\n}\n\nreq = urllib.request.Request(\n    \"http://localhost:11434/api/chat\",\n    data=json.dumps(payload).encode(),\n    headers={\"Content-Type\": \"application/json\"},\n    method=\"POST\"\n)\n\nwith urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=180) as r:\n    result = json.loads(r.read())\n    print(result[\"message\"][\"content\"])\nPY","timeout":200}}],"stopReason":"toolUse","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":30680,"output":614,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":31294,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773966829890}}
