{"type":"message","id":"edce42fc","parentId":"7beda7fb","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:34:53.051Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"ollama_call_ca83efcf-b025-43ed-b2e1-ce54a72f8d4c","toolName":"process","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Based on the analysis of the provided LinkedIn profile HTML (decoded from base64), here is the breakdown of the posts identified in the activity feed, featured section, and highlights.\n\n### **Identified Posts**\n\n1.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Highlight)\n    *   **Topic:** Work Anniversary (\"Yosef is celebrating 5 years at Nava Healthcare Recruitment\")\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston (Attributed to profile, likely system-generated but appears as profile activity)\n    *   **Activity ID:** `urn:li:activity:7438060739019554816`\n\n2.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Featured)\n    *   **Topic:** The YoJoeShow Podcast - Episode 13 (Uncensored discussion on various topics)\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston (Co-Host)\n    *   **Activity ID:** `urn:li:activity:7336266318670610434`\n\n3.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Featured)\n    *   **Topic:** NurseSphere (Long-Term Solution to Nursing Shortage, division of Nava Healthcare)\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston\n    *   **Media ID:** `1745518283625`\n\n4.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Featured)\n    *   **Topic:** Reclaimix (Reclaim Costs, Talent, Stability by Nava Healthcare Recruitment)\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston\n    *   **Media ID:** `1745517628372`\n\n5.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Activity Feed)\n    *   **Topic:** Thought Leadership (\"Patients read billboards, but clinicians read the room...\")\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston\n    *   **Activity ID:** `urn:li:activity:7432001387011457024`\n\n### **Search for Repost Indicators**\n*   **Tiny Manyonga:** The name \"Tiny Manyonga\" appears twice in the HTML `<head>` section (`<title>Tiny Manyonga | LinkedIn</title>`), likely due to page metadata or connection loading. However, there are **no post containers** in the feed body where Tiny Manyonga is listed as the original author of a content item reposted by Yosef.\n*   **Nava Healthcare Recruitment:** While multiple posts *mention* Nava Healthcare Recruitment (as Yosef's company), the post headers consistently identify **Yosef Roston** as the author. There are no HTML classes or text indicators (e.g., \"Reposted by\", `urn:li:share:`) suggesting these are reposts from the Company Page rather than original posts by Yosef.\n*   **Other Sources:** No other external authors were identified in the post headers.\n\n### **Final Counts**\n\n*   **Total original posts by Yosef:** 5\n*   **Total reposts from Tiny:** 0\n*   **Total reposts from Nava:** 0\n*   **Total reposts from other sources:** 0\n\n**Total Posts Identified:** 5\n\nProcess exited with code 0."}],"details":{"status":"completed","sessionId":"grand-shoal","exitCode":0,"aggregated":"Based on the analysis of the provided LinkedIn profile HTML (decoded from base64), here is the breakdown of the posts identified in the activity feed, featured section, and highlights.\n\n### **Identified Posts**\n\n1.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Highlight)\n    *   **Topic:** Work Anniversary (\"Yosef is celebrating 5 years at Nava Healthcare Recruitment\")\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston (Attributed to profile, likely system-generated but appears as profile activity)\n    *   **Activity ID:** `urn:li:activity:7438060739019554816`\n\n2.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Featured)\n    *   **Topic:** The YoJoeShow Podcast - Episode 13 (Uncensored discussion on various topics)\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston (Co-Host)\n    *   **Activity ID:** `urn:li:activity:7336266318670610434`\n\n3.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Featured)\n    *   **Topic:** NurseSphere (Long-Term Solution to Nursing Shortage, division of Nava Healthcare)\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston\n    *   **Media ID:** `1745518283625`\n\n4.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Featured)\n    *   **Topic:** Reclaimix (Reclaim Costs, Talent, Stability by Nava Healthcare Recruitment)\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston\n    *   **Media ID:** `1745517628372`\n\n5.  **Post Type:** Original Post (Activity Feed)\n    *   **Topic:** Thought Leadership (\"Patients read billboards, but clinicians read the room...\")\n    *   **Original Author:** Yosef Roston\n    *   **Activity ID:** `urn:li:activity:7432001387011457024`\n\n### **Search for Repost Indicators**\n*   **Tiny Manyonga:** The name \"Tiny Manyonga\" appears twice in the HTML `<head>` section (`<title>Tiny Manyonga | LinkedIn</title>`), likely due to page metadata or connection loading. However, there are **no post containers** in the feed body where Tiny Manyonga is listed as the original author of a content item reposted by Yosef.\n*   **Nava Healthcare Recruitment:** While multiple posts *mention* Nava Healthcare Recruitment (as Yosef's company), the post headers consistently identify **Yosef Roston** as the author. There are no HTML classes or text indicators (e.g., \"Reposted by\", `urn:li:share:`) suggesting these are reposts from the Company Page rather than original posts by Yosef.\n*   **Other Sources:** No other external authors were identified in the post headers.\n\n### **Final Counts**\n\n*   **Total original posts by Yosef:** 5\n*   **Total reposts from Tiny:** 0\n*   **Total reposts from Nava:** 0\n*   **Total reposts from other sources:** 0\n\n**Total Posts Identified:** 5\n","name":"python3 <<'PY'"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1773966893045}}
{"type":"message","id":"f3abad60","parentId":"edce42fc","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:35:05.335Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Here's what the HTML analysis reveals — with important caveats:\n\n---\n\n## From HTML Analysis: Yosef's Profile\n\n**What the HTML shows:**\n- **5 posts visible** in the feed\n- Work anniversary (system-generated)\n- YoJoeShow Podcast Ep 13 (Featured)\n- NurseSphere (Featured)  \n- Reclaimix (Featured)\n- \"Patients read billboards...\" (your post that Yosef amplified)\n\n**Problem with the HTML dump:**\nThe HTML doesn't show the \"reposted from Tiny Manyonga\" labels that Tiny's screenshots showed. This suggests either:\n1. The HTML dump was taken from a view where reposts display as Yosef's posts\n2. The dump missed the attribution metadata\n\n**What CAN be inferred from the HTML:**\n- Total visible posts: ~5-6\n- Yosef writes/shares content in his voice (founder/operator tone)\n- Content clusters: podcast, NurseSphere, Reclaimix, thought leadership\n- The \"Patients read billboards\" post appears in the feed (this was originally your content that Yosef amplified)\n\n---\n\n## Key Insight\n\n**The HTML doesn't differentiate between \"Yosef original\" vs \"Yosef reposted from Tiny\"** — both show as Yosef posting. The distinction exists in LinkedIn's UI but wasn't captured in the HTML dump we analyzed.\n\nThis is different from the previous Gemma analysis which identified specific repost patterns. The discrepancy suggests:\n- Some posts were Tiny-written-for-Yosef (shows as Yosef)\n- Some were Tiny-posted-on-Tiny-profile-then-Yosef-reposted (shows as Yosef in this dump)\n\nWould you like me to look at your actual screenshots to count manually? That would be more reliable than trying to parse this HTML dump."}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":31976,"output":655,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":32631,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773966905334}}
