{"type":"message","id":"b2f170e0","parentId":"cf394d1f","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:49:07.622Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"## ✅ Playwright Installed Successfully\n\n| Step | Status |\n|------|--------|\n| Backup config | ✅ `~/TinyBackUp/20260320_playwright/` |\n| Install Playwright | ✅ |\n| Install Chromium | ✅ |\n| Test click/scroll | ✅ Working |\n| Script created | ✅ `scripts/playwright_browser.py` |\n| TOOLS.md updated | ✅ |\n\n### New Capability\n\nI can now:\n- `python3 scripts/playwright_browser.py <url> screenshot` — full screenshot\n- `python3 scripts/playwright_browser.py <url> scroll` — scroll to bottom\n- `python3 scripts/playwright_browser.py <url> click \"#selector\"` — click element\n- `python3 scripts/playwright_browser.py <url> html` — get page HTML\n\n---\n\n### Pending Items (from memory)\n\n1. **X post from Draft 001** — Still missing, should derive from \"The Incentive Trap\"\n2. **Resume process teaching** — NurseSphere / LTC facilities angle\n3. **Draft 002** — LTC + NurseSphere (requires Tiny's input on NurseSphere process)\n\nReady for next step. Want me to tackle the X post from Draft 001, or continue with something else?"}],"stopReason":"stop","api":"ollama","provider":"ollama","model":"minimax-m2.5:cloud","usage":{"input":43129,"output":273,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":43402,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"timestamp":1773967747621}}
{"type":"message","id":"caad30d6","parentId":"b2f170e0","timestamp":"2026-03-20T00:52:14.761Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Sender (untrusted metadata):\n```json\n{\n  \"label\": \"openclaw-tui (gateway-client)\",\n  \"id\": \"gateway-client\",\n  \"name\": \"openclaw-tui\",\n  \"username\": \"openclaw-tui\"\n}\n```\n\n[Fri 2026-03-20 02:52 GMT+2] I need you to revisit my profile and Yosef's Profile on LinkedIn to check for relevant posts. But before we do that, do we still not have an option for you to have persistent profiles on your WSL profile so I can give you log in details and you only log in once? Also, back up memories because I am about to compact the context."}],"timestamp":1773967934758}}
